autoRateDrivers Expression Set
autoRateVehicles Expression Set

This expression set rates all vehicles to be insured. It includes variables, constants, and calculation steps. We expect you'll create your own expression set to rate vehicles for your auto insurance products.

The meat of the expression set is its calculation steps:

* Does a matrix lookup on the value of the car.
* Does a matrix lookup on the car symbol.
* Does a matrix lookup on the year of the car.
* Does a matrix lookup to see if the car uses alternative fuel.
* Does a matrix lookup to see whether the car has stability controls.
* ...
* Calculates the premium for Rental Car coverage.

The autoRateVehiclesLookup Tables use lookup tables to identify ratings for your auto insurance products. You can modify these lookup tables to reflect your ratings.
title: Auto Insurance Rate Calculation
